*13. Union Magdalena         26       5       7      14     18-34   17
*14. Deportes Tolima         26       1      12      13     18-34   14

Note:

Atlético Nacional and Deportivo Cali both with 37 points had to play extra
matches to decide the champion of Torneo Apertura 1974:

First Leg  [Jul 11, Medellín]
Nacional   3-2 Cali

Second Leg [Jul 14, Cali]
Cali       2-1 Nacional

Then Nacional was proclaimed champion of Torneo Apertura because of their
largest number of won matches.


   
